articles.title: Ursula von der Leyen: EU Commission chief says free trade deal with India could come this year - BBC.com
articles.description: The two sides discussed ways to further strengthen the Indo-EU strategic partnership.
articles.content:
The head of the European Commission, Ursula von der Leyen said EU and India were pushing to get a free trade agreement during this year.
